-- Sinocop to Raise HK$44 Million in Placing for Working Capital, Expansion
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-10-21T13:42:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-21/sinocop-to-raise-hk-44-million-in-placing-for-working-capital-expansion.html
Sinocop Resources Holdings Ltd . said
it will raise as much as HK$44 million for working capital and
potential future investments through a private placing of 110
million shares at 40 Hong Kong cents each.  Yicko Securities Ltd. will be conducting the best-effort
placing for a commission of 3 percent, Sinocop said in a Hong
Kong stock exchange filing today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  